Package com.constantcontact.components.contacts

Class Summary
Address Represents a single Address of a Contact for the Contact Service in Constant Contact.
AddressType Address type constants for the Contact Service in Constant Contact.
Use this whenever an address type field is expected.
Most likely, will be for Address.getAddressType() and Address.setAddressType(String)
Contact Represents a single Contact for the Contact Service in Constant Contact.
Contact.ActionBy Action By constants for the Contact type in Constant Contact.
ContactList Represents a Contacts List for the Contact Service in Constant Contact.
It may contain from one to many contacts.
Doesn't actually store any contacts! BUT each Contact has an internal reference to the list(s) it is a member of.
That "list of lists" can be retrieved using Contact.getLists()
ContactListStatus Contact lists status constants for the ContactList Service in Constant Contact.
Use this whenever a contact list status field is expected.
Most likely, will be for ContactList.getStatus() and ContactList.setStatus(String)
CustomField Custom Field for the Contact Service in Constant Contact.
Used in Contact.
CustomField.CustomFieldName Custom fields names constants for the usage of CustomField.
Holds constants for values from CustomField1 to CustomField15.
EmailAddress Email Address info from a Contact for the Contact Service in Constant Contact.
EmailAddress.ConfirmStatus Confirmation status constants for the usage of EmailAddress.
EmailAddress.OptInSource Opt In Source constants for the usage of EmailAddress.
Note Note info from a Contact for the Contact Service in Constant Contact.
 

Enum Summary
Contact.Status Status enum for the Contact type in Constant Contact.
